#. <section class="sutta" id="sn23.46"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn23.46:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 23"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 23"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn23.46:0.2"
msgid "4. Upanisinnavagga"
msgstr "4. Sitting Close"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn23.46:0.3"
msgid "46. Nirodhadhammasutta"
msgstr "46. Liable To Cease"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn23.46:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthinidānaṃ."
msgstr "At Sāvatthī."

msgctxt "sn23.46:1.2"
msgid "Ekamantaṃ nisinnaṃ kho āyasmantaṃ rādhaṃ bhagavā etadavoca:"
msgstr "When Venerable Rādha was seated to one side, the Buddha said to him:"

msgctxt "sn23.46:1.3"
msgid ""
"“yo kho, rādha, nirodhadhammo; tatra te chando pahātabbo, rāgo pahātabbo, "
"chandarāgo pahātabbo."
msgstr ""
"“Rādha, you should give up any desire, any greed, any desire and greed for "
"whatever is liable to cease."

msgctxt "sn23.46:1.4"
msgid "Ko ca, rādha, nirodhadhammo?"
msgstr "And what is liable to cease?"

msgctxt "sn23.46:1.5"
msgid ""
"Rūpaṃ kho, rādha, nirodhadhammo; tatra te chando pahātabbo, rāgo pahātabbo, "
"chandarāgo pahātabbo."
msgstr ""
"Form is liable to cease. You should give up any desire, any greed, any "
"desire and greed for it."

msgctxt "sn23.46:1.6"
msgid "Vedanā … pe …"
msgstr "Feeling …"

msgctxt "sn23.46:1.7"
msgid "saññā … pe …"
msgstr "Perception …"

msgctxt "sn23.46:1.8"
msgid "saṅkhārā … pe …"
msgstr "Choices …"

msgctxt "sn23.46:1.9"
msgid ""
"viññāṇaṃ nirodhadhammo; tatra te chando pahātabbo, rāgo pahātabbo, "
"chandarāgo pahātabbo."
msgstr ""
"Consciousness is liable to cease. You should give up any desire, any greed, "
"any desire and greed for it."

msgctxt "sn23.46:1.10"
msgid ""
"Yo kho, rādha, nirodhadhammo; tatra te chando pahātabbo, rāgo pahātabbo, "
"chandarāgo pahātabbo”ti."
msgstr ""
"You should give up any desire, any greed, any desire and greed for whatever "
"is liable to cease.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn23.46:1.11"
msgid "Upanisinnavaggo catuttho."
msgstr ""

#. </p><blockquote class="uddanagatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn23.46:2.1"
msgid "Māro ca māradhammo ca,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn23.46:2.2"
msgid "Aniccena apare duve;"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn23.46:2.3"
msgid "Dukkhena ca duve vuttā,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn23.46:2.4"
msgid "Anattena tatheva ca;"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn23.46:2.5"
msgid "Khayavayasamudayaṃ,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn23.46:2.6"
msgid "Nirodhadhammena dvādasāti."
msgstr ""

#. </p></blockquote><p class="endsutta">
msgctxt "sn23.46:2.7"
msgid "Rādhasaṃyuttaṃ samattaṃ."
msgstr "The Linked Discourses with Rādha are complete."
